{"tid":158582,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"勁乞人憎既大陸親戚霸左我屋企住，求救","createTime":"2017-03-16T11:19:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-16T15:39:20.000Z","uid":69662,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0b9c38d758adeefc96166e388a9601e893f00fd9","tid":158582,"uid":69662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T11:19:57.000Z","msg":"文略長，請見諒<br />\n<br />\n話說一年前，因為有屋企人搬左出去，就空左個房，呀媽見間房咁大，打算租出去。點知，當時有個大陸住既堂哥同佢老婆過嚟探我地，見到間房咁大，又有海景睇，加上佢地嗰陣批左可以嚟香港定居，就打算用HKD6000同我呀媽租，但家務洗衫三餐都要包埋。<br />\n<br />\n當時呀媽梗係諗俾自己人好過俾外人住，況且呀爸又好錫我堂哥，就應承左，當時我地都諗屋企多人會熱鬧啲，所以我地都好開心。<br />\n<br />\n點知，咁先係惡夢既開始<br />\n<br />\n初初佢地一家三口(因為有個4歲既仔)入嚟住左幾個月，同我地都幾好相處，後來佢老婆就開始嚟料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個女人之後搵到份工，就諗住叫我呀媽幫手湊女，租唔加都算啦，後來又嫌我呀媽湊得唔好，又冇營養，但我呀媽好比心機湊佢個女，日日營養餐，講真我地又唔係有錢人，點會餐餐大魚大肉。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但就佢地覺得香港既常餐係零食，大魚大肉先係正餐，入得嚟香港住，唔該跟番香港既規舉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲因少少野同呀媽嘈，我地叫佢地搬又唔肯，佢地仲要日日大大聲鬧個仔，鬧到隔籬鄰舍都怕左我地。鬧還鬧丫，日日咁鬧法真係好騷擾，又做唔到野，又休息唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟著佢地就自己煮自己食，點知冇問我呀媽就拎哂佢買既餸煮俾佢嗰家三口食。我呀媽見到，都扮唔知，因為佢地兩公婆日日巳經鬧到好煩，最後咪連我地收起左啲山珍海味都消失左<br />\n<br />\n其實我屋企有婉轉叫佢地搬，我呀媽仲好細心咁拎左公屋申請表俾佢地，但佢地完全冇打算搬走，呀爸又好鐘意佢地，真心，如果佢地好既話冇打算叫佢地搬，但同佢地住真係好辛苦。各位巴絲，有冇咩方法可以令大家好做啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f7b99864cc62836a94817e463405e3ef5e8f9c7","tid":158582,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T11:20:54.000Z","msg":"TLDR"},{"pid":"cd53b80ddd93d496e9f427c239a347ce1b7e1290","tid":158582,"uid":69662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T11:22:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>TLDR</blockquote><br />\nhihi<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05857bc5cbfa6b13124c0378c6e0c37275295db8","tid":158582,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T11:26:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>TLDR</blockquote><br />\nhihi<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"effd6e8dcdd51b1b052282455896fa58a1211b3b","tid":158582,"uid":41292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T11:26:43.000Z","msg":"整個租客需知比佢地喇"},{"pid":"0d210d4ec8fa5de7eee883637bf80d0073343751","tid":158582,"uid":4242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T11:38:02.000Z","msg":"換鎖 / 加租"},{"pid":"ce4388643ffb7e7fe9a6f2846a66865f22cdccdd","tid":158582,"uid":54597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T11:53:37.000Z","msg":"你呀爸無撚用<br />\n一係佢出手叫人走，一係佢出錢請個工人服恃佢地<br />\n有咩理由要自己老婆服恃人地成家，貼錢又受氣"},{"pid":"6a286ff5774500d7c7dcfd9e1a0c118509f52287","tid":158582,"uid":69662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T12:43:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你呀爸無撚用<br />\n一係佢出手叫人走，一係佢出錢請個工人服恃佢地<br />\n有咩理由要自己老婆服恃人地成家，貼錢又受氣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唉 我地有同呀爸講過 但佢真係聽下就算 <br />\n其實有用過好多方法去同佢地講 <br />\n我試過發到好大脾氣 點知佢地話我白痴底能 浪費呀媽供我讀U既錢 <br />\n<br />\n真係吹脹 明明佢地霸左我間屋"},{"pid":"3be33cf672e144f9f80060c5ed6fd6de01322a3c","tid":158582,"uid":69662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T12:44:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>換鎖 / 加租</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唉 佢地而家同呀媽講價比少啲 話而家三餐自己煮"},{"pid":"9228223b31ba6491b84700dc90f1cff4f05d9622","tid":158582,"uid":973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T12:46:00.000Z","msg":"講堅成件事最重要既人係你老豆"},{"pid":"34e3510e775a53d8110b2717f32b3e30fcb04d58","tid":158582,"uid":38825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T12:48:50.000Z","msg":"同你老豆講：你搞唔掂我就同娘親搬，等佢慢慢招呼幾隻蝗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae5a91fdaffd30fbd929bf864a291f65f7d1fc2e","tid":158582,"uid":52591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T12:49:08.000Z","msg":"你係獨生女？你老豆明顯當左你堂哥係佢半邊仔，遲下真係分埋身家比佢<br />\n<br />\n如果你係仔，咁都忍得真係食屎大，係就搞大佢，同你老豆老母講有佢地無你"},{"pid":"2d8f3d0abf815775f522c13d1c0eb11aa46b289c","tid":158582,"uid":69662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:14:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係獨生女？你老豆明顯當左你堂哥係佢半邊仔，遲下真係分埋身家比佢<br />\n<br />\n如果你係仔，咁都忍得真係食屎大，係就搞大佢，同你老豆老母講有佢地無你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係絲，有個呀哥，不過搬左，老豆由我小學開始真係冇咩理過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fac3d2ba2e3430fc31c19087dc57f42d79e72a7","tid":158582,"uid":69662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:16:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同你老豆講：你搞唔掂我就同娘親搬，等佢慢慢招呼幾隻蝗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有講過，不過仲有兩年先grad,有工先可以搬到，大個都會同娘親住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb4258e2cc87a707be6f89e1e5d8d8cf2e150c84","tid":158582,"uid":69662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:18:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講堅成件事最重要既人係你老豆</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嘈到咁佢冇出過聲，但暫時都要同嗰對乞人憎既夫婦相處"},{"pid":"00a96d5255a51cfbc32d8b661137813800b672d1","tid":158582,"uid":41205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:19:30.000Z","msg":"你啊爸冇完<br />\n<br />\n佢地一定唔會走<br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"cfee769487c1ae076f3eda7f1c56977e037f5d24","tid":158582,"uid":41205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:19:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你啊爸冇用<br />\n<br />\n佢地一定唔會走<br />\n<br />\n完</blockquote>"},{"pid":"462f5d99aade6f2bbf11a47d238c29202c498f57","tid":158582,"uid":59684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:21:51.000Z","msg":"換左把鎖佢"},{"pid":"7df9b458f3135d4cff27a92acda05ec474ee61b1","tid":158582,"uid":41205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:23:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你係獨生女？你老豆明顯當左你堂哥係佢半邊仔，遲下真係分埋身家比佢<br />\n<br />\n如果你係仔，咁都忍得真係食屎大，係就搞大佢，同你老豆老母講有佢地無你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係絲，有個呀哥，不過搬左，老豆由我小學開始真係冇咩理過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇死你老豆係60+重男輕女冇學識平時最叻就賭馬仔既廢老啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddaaa6d4ca3d3d79f99c098a891e194c931e7ba4","tid":158582,"uid":59684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:25:37.000Z","msg":"日日曬啲恐佈血腥鬼片或一係啲南京大屠殺片"},{"pid":"3e5b7b7a9838fd591b806816134f7e2c05c48d7b","tid":158582,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:27:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />整獲野俾佢地嘆"},{"pid":"33c82c694cccc2963df27e142922e1c0cdb44c77","tid":158582,"uid":59684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:28:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日日<span style=\"color: red;\">睇</span>曬啲恐佈血腥鬼片或一係啲南京大屠殺片嚇到佢地走 人形蜈蚣2 下水道美人魚 要播大聲啲 電視睇</blockquote>"},{"pid":"54f835ace6025e5036d0e3de4d4ece227dc826d5","tid":158582,"uid":59684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:28:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>日日<span style=\"color: red;\">睇</span>曬啲恐佈血腥鬼片或一係啲南京大屠殺片嚇到佢地走 人形蜈蚣2 下水道美人魚 要播大聲啲 電視睇</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"211bd1ecde8f317f423aca4ebde16f21921d89aa","tid":158582,"uid":59684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:29:41.000Z","msg":"扮撞邪嚇到佢地疌"},{"pid":"5d160d85b54fa34f34d687217827c6a24a35ac72","tid":158582,"uid":59684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:31:10.000Z","msg":"日日夜睌播歌嘈死佢"}]}